             <h1 className="text-5xl font-black text-slate-900 mb-6 tracking-tight">Booking confirmed!</h1>
             <p className="text-xl text-slate-500 font-medium mb-16 max-w-xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
               An instant confirmation has been sent to your mobile. Please arrive 10 minutes early.
             </p>
             <div className="bg-white p-10 rounded-[48px] border border-slate-100 shadow-3xl text-left relative overflow-hidden">
                <div className="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-brand-50 rounded-full blur-3xl opacity-50"></div>
                <h3 className="font-black text-slate-900 border-b border-slate-100 pb-6 mb-8 uppercase text-xs tracking-[0.2em] flex items-center gap-3">
